2064.subject: HPWE
2064.descrlong: Studies scientific concepts of nutrition related to nutritional needs, practices, and problems throughout the life cycle.  Emphasizes evidence-based, scientific nutritional information, personal decision making, and education of individuals/groups toward health promotion and disease prevention.
